	(text "tr (rise time): 1000 ns (I2C spec)\nCb (bus capacitance): ~50 pF\nVDD: 3.3 V\nVOL: 0.4 V (I2C spec)\nIOL: 3 mA (I2C spec)\n\nRpmax (max pull-up value): tr / (0.8473 * Cb) = ~23 kOhm\nRpmin (min pull-up value): (VDD - VOL) / IOL = ~1 kOhm "
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 244.348 22.352 0)
